NAME
    List::Util::Uniq - List utilities related to finding unique items

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of List::Util::Uniq (from Perl
    distribution List-Util-Uniq), released on 2018-02-21.

FUNCTIONS
    Not exported by default but exportable.

  uniq_adj(@list) => LIST
    Remove *adjacent* duplicates from list, i.e. behave more like Unix
    utility's uniq instead of List::MoreUtils's "uniq" function, e.g.

     my @res = uniq(1, 4, 4, 3, 1, 1, 2); # 1, 4, 3, 1, 2

  uniq_adj_ci(@list) => LIST
    Like "uniq_adj" except case-insensitive.

  uniq_ci(@list) => LIST
    Like "List::MoreUtils"' "uniq" except case-insensitive.

